      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Star colt HOLLYWOOD STRIP (7) took his record to 12 from 13 when cruising home in the Nutrien Classic Sales Race Series 3CG Final last start, stretching his unbeaten run at this venue to three. Draws deeper but easily won the Wagga Cup from a similar barrier three back. Hard to go past him. HES FROM HEAVEN NZ (8) has raced twice this prep and has filled a minor placing on each occasion. Beaten only 3.5m at Listed level first up then recorded another strong performance behind Group 1 winner Bay Of Biscay. Must overcome a very wide draw but has won two of three third-up attempts so should be close to his peak. NOVANTA RISING (3) draws well for his return and should be ready to go off two nice trials, winning the latest. MESSAGE BANK (4) jumps in grade but has won three of his last four and has only once been beaten in seven tries at this distance.",
